# Line-ending normalization across Mac (mac-dev) <-> Windows (capture-pc).
# Prevents CRLF drift when the Windows capture PC edits tracked files
# (the pc-drift-20260618 bundle mangled whichdevice.py: em-dash -> hyphen,
# cp -> copy). Text files normalize to LF in the repo; Windows shell scripts
# keep CRLF so PowerShell/.bat render correctly on the PC.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.ps1 text eol=crlf
*.bat text eol=crlf
*.cmd text eol=crlf
